        {
            "title": "乘聯分會：上月內地新能源車零售量按年升79.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">乘聯分會公布，今年2月份新能源乘用車市場零售68.6萬輛，按年增79.7%；今年首兩個月累計零售143萬輛，增長35.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/05/Biden_China_Tariffs_24135035976797.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/05/Biden_China_Tariffs_24135035976797.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上月新能源乘用車批發銷量達83萬輛，按年亦升79.6%，首兩月累計批發171.9萬輛，按年增48%。2月份出口11.8萬輛，按年增27.8%，首兩月累計出口25.7萬輛，增長28.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">產量方面，2月新能源乘用車生產達81.9萬輛，按年升85.9%，首兩月累計生產175.9萬輛，增長48.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">2月份新能源車國內零售滲透率49.5%，較去年同期滲透率提升15個百分點，其中新勢力市佔率19.9%，小米(01810)等品牌拉動新勢力市佔率年增2.6個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於全國乘用車市場方面，2月份零售138.6萬輛，按年升26%；今年首兩月累計零售317.9萬輛，較去年同期成長1.2%。 </p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14765900-%e4%b9%98%e8%81%af%e5%88%86%e6%9c%83%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90%e8%bb%8a%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8779-7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Economy_704.jpg.webp",
