            "title": "滬指收跌6點 深指跌幅收窄至0.17% 芯片股個別發展 寒武紀反彈中芯則再回",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國上月通脹數據遜預期，內地股市借勢回吐，但午後跌勢放緩。芯片股個別發展，AI芯片概念股寒武紀(688256.SH)逆市反彈。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/寒武紀_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/寒武紀_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開不足1點後反覆下跌，只有初段曾短暫微升，午後曾跌破早市低位，在跌25點、見3347點後形勢才見改善，由低位拾級反彈；滬指收報3366點，跌幅收窄至跌6點或0.19%，成交5950.26億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指早市同樣呈拾級下滑狀態，初段雖然曾倒升最多52點，衝上10896點已成全日高位，午後跌幅最多擴大至96點，低見10747點，其後跌幅反覆收窄；深指收報10825點，僅跌18點或0.17%，成交9106.33億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌15點或0.39%，以3928點收市；創業板指數跌5點或0.25%，報2199點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"上海復旦官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/01385-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"上海復旦官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/01385-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">上海復旦官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅芯片股互有升跌，寒武紀午後動力提升，收漲3.87%，報779元；復旦微電(01385)A股(688385.SH)也升3.37%，報52.15元。相反，中芯A股(688981.SH)則沽壓未消，收跌1.26%，報95.66元；華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)也跌0.75%，報53.98元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地電訊股午後仍然受壓，中國電信(00728)A股(601728.SH)跌幅擴大至3.16%，報7.96元；中國聯通(00762)A股(600050.SH)跌2.96%，報6.22元；中國移動(00941)A股(600941.SH)則跌1.8%，報106.64元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14765598-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c6%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84%e8%87%b30-17-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e5%80%8b%e5%88%a5%e7%99%bc%e5%b1%95-%e5%af%92%e6%ad%a6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 15:10:49",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
